-Oh! My God!


480
00:22:58.105 --> 00:23:00.063
-[Carlo] Yeah.
-I'll be here too.


481
00:23:00.146 --> 00:23:01.480
-Yeah?
-[Emilio] Mm-hmm.


482
00:23:01.563 --> 00:23:04.646
-You too?
-Not because of a cancellation, though. I…


483
00:23:04.730 --> 00:23:07.188
