484
00:23:08.355 --> 00:23:09.563
Call me immature if you like,

485
00:23:09.646 --> 00:23:12.688
but I can still feel that umbilical cord
firmly attached to mom.


486
00:23:12.771 --> 00:23:15.313
-The umbilical cord, hear that?
