508
00:23:59.188 --> 00:24:00.146
Yes, same here.

509
00:24:00.230 --> 00:24:04.230
Even if we didn't see her very much,
but I really and truly loved her.


510
00:24:04.313 --> 00:24:07.646
Yes, I was always very fond
of Aunt Tea. Yeah.


511
00:24:07.730 --> 00:24:08.771
Ah!

512
00:24:09.438 --> 00:24:10.563
Oh, yes. [laughs]

513
00:24:10.646 --> 00:24:12.855
