514
00:24:12.938 --> 00:24:15.021
She actually left us
quite a bit of inheritance.


515
00:24:15.105 --> 00:24:17.021
-Quite a huge bit. [chuckles]
-Mm.


516
00:24:17.730 --> 00:24:20.188
-Ah. Oh yeah? Is that so?
