572
00:26:58.313 --> 00:26:59.563
[people cheering]

573
00:26:59.646 --> 00:27:01.855
Now let's all toast to Aunt Tea!

574
00:27:01.938 --> 00:27:04.896
[all chanting] Aunt Tea! Aunt Tea!

575
00:27:04.980 --> 00:27:09.188
Aunt Tea! Aunt Tea! Aunt Tea!

576
00:27:09.271 --> 00:27:11.313
They don't wanna be around us anymore.

577
00:27:11.938 --> 00:27:13.938
