What did we do?

578
00:27:14.021 --> 00:27:16.605
'Cause I just really
didn't see this coming.


579
00:27:17.730 --> 00:27:19.938
We used to do so many things together.

580
00:27:21.230 --> 00:27:24.730
You remember Greece, hon?
All of us in a tent together.


581
00:27:25.646 --> 00:27:27.105
-[Carlo inhales deeply]
-Hmm.


582
00:27:27.188 --> 00:27:29.646
We could do nice things together,
the two of us now.


583
00:27:29.730 --> 00:27:30.938
