584
00:27:31.646 --> 00:27:33.938
Stuff like getting undressed, lying down…

585
00:27:34.021 --> 00:27:35.271
An MRI?

586
00:27:36.063 --> 00:27:37.813
Don't be morbid, Anna.

587
00:27:37.896 --> 00:27:41.896
Look, Carlo, really, I'm just
not in the mood to celebrate anything.


588
00:27:41.980 --> 00:27:44.021
Let me remind you,
we haven't done it since Halloween,


589
00:27:44.105 --> 00:27:45.480
a year ago, maybe more.

590
00:27:45.563 --> 00:27:46.896
