was remarkable.


593
00:27:50.855 --> 00:27:53.021
Solid work. Stamina.

594
00:27:53.105 --> 00:27:54.105
[sighs loudly]

595
00:27:55.355 --> 00:27:56.313
[inhales deeply]

596
00:27:56.396 --> 00:27:59.021
-[Anna] And by the way, you were right.
-About the kids?


597
00:27:59.105 --> 00:28:02.271
Yeah, about the fact that they'd show up
just because of the money.


598
00:28:02.355 --> 00:28:03.188
[Carlo sighs]

599
00:28:03.271 --> 00:28:06.146
