628
00:29:18.146 --> 00:29:22.021
<i>♪ Adorable illusion and I cannot hide ♪</i>

629
00:29:22.646 --> 00:29:26.938
<i>♪ I'm the one you're using</i>
<i>Please don't push me aside ♪</i>


630
00:29:27.021 --> 00:29:29.521
<i>♪ We coulda made it cruising, yeah ♪</i>

631
00:29:38.938 --> 00:29:41.271
-[Carlo] Can I get in it?
-[man] Knock yourself out.


632
00:29:47.105 --> 00:29:48.855
-[Carlo grunts]
-[Anna] Hey.


633
00:29:48.938 --> 00:29:49.896
[grunts]

634
00:29:50.480 --> 00:29:51.813
How do you feel in it?

635
00:29:51.896 --> 00:29:54.688
You'll need a hydraulic pump
to suck me out of here.


636
00:29:54.771 --> 00:29:56.271
But it feels like heaven, huh?

637
00:29:56.896 --> 00:29:59.438
-[man] How long you wanna rent it?
-Uh…


638
00:30:00.021 --> 00:30:01.438
Well, until Christmas.

639
00:30:01.521 --> 00:30:02.521
Okay.

640
00:30:02.605 --> 00:30:05.355
And… what kind of insurance
should I pay you?


641
00:30:05.938 --> 00:30:07.146
Let's just say, you damage her,

642
00:30:07.230 --> 00:30:09.021
I'll cut your balls off
and feed 'em to the dog.


643
00:30:09.105 --> 00:30:11.855
That's… That's quite reassuring to hear.

644
00:30:12.521 --> 00:30:14.855
-And that's a high deductible.
-[Carlo] Uh-huh.


645
00:30:16.188 --> 00:30:18.855
[woman] So, you're supposed to leave
for Amsterdam on Thursday


646
00:30:18.938 --> 00:30:19.980
and return on Monday.

647
00:30:20.063 --> 00:30:21.980
-Okay. Fine by me, no problem.
-[knocking on door]


648
00:30:22.688 --> 00:30:24.230
Yeah? Come in.

649
00:30:24.313 --> 00:30:26.230
Great. Here he is. Come, come.

650
00:30:26.813 --> 00:30:28.188
Anyway, no problem at all.

651
00:30:28.271 --> 00:30:29.521
-Here?
-[Azeglio] Mm-hmm.


652
00:30:30.396 --> 00:30:31.355
Thank you.

653
00:30:32.021 --> 00:30:32.980
-[Azeglio] So?
-Mm.


654
00:30:33.063 --> 00:30:34.396
-[Azeglio] What's up?
-Huh?


655
00:30:35.271 --> 00:30:36.105
So how are you?

656
00:30:36.188 --> 00:30:39.021
[inhales sharply] Oh, I'm fine.
All good, thanks, yeah.


657
00:30:39.521 --> 00:30:43.396
