is that you're improving finally.


668
00:31:04.896 --> 00:31:07.896
And so finally, I can offer you
a position as a…


669
00:31:09.480 --> 00:31:10.480
a partner.

670
00:31:10.563 --> 00:31:13.313
Mm? We'd be partners. 
That sound good?

671
00:31:14.896 --> 00:31:16.855
-Are you serious?
