672
00:31:16.938 --> 00:31:18.605
I'm done trying to mess with you.

673
00:31:20.313 --> 00:31:21.230
If you want, now,

674
00:31:21.730 --> 00:31:24.438
it's me and you who'll be
messing with all the others.


675
00:31:24.980 --> 00:31:26.355
You know? [laughs]

676
00:31:26.438 --> 00:31:27.896
Well, it wouldn't be that bad.

677
00:31:27.980 --> 00:31:31.230
Obviously, you'd chip in a small amount,
let's say, just a small investment


678
00:31:31.313 --> 00:31:35.230
to become a partner, just as I did,
way back when I first started here. Hmm?


679
00:31:35.313 --> 00:31:36.855
Of course. Of course.

680
00:31:36.938 --> 00:31:38.813
There. Also, because I know…

681
00:31:39.980 --> 00:31:41.230
I mean, I heard that…

682
00:31:42.105 --> 00:31:43.813
[phone ringing in distance]

683
00:31:44.813 --> 00:31:46.396
[breathes deeply]

684
00:31:46.480 --> 00:31:48.730
Rumor has it you have the means, now.

685
00:31:48.813 --> 00:31:51.146
-So…
-Oh, I get it, I get it.


686
00:31:51.855 --> 00:31:54.980
However, that money's not even mine.
It's my father's.


687
00:31:55.063 --> 00:31:56.688
Uh, and he's a very…

688
00:31:56.771 --> 00:31:59.521
very self-restrained person,
to say the very least.


689
00:32:00.230 --> 00:32:01.605
Let's just say he's the kind of guy

690
00:32:01.688 --> 00:32:03.563
